skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: phil's osophy
des:
Anxious about your first born going off to college? Want to impart some wisdom gleaned from whimsical observations & life lessons? If so this may (or may not) be the skill for you! 

Phil's-Osophy offers you all of this and more! Phil Dunphy, noted Realtor and amateur magician, is offering this exclusive Alexa skill in the hopes of inspiring the masses.

With such classics as, "Dance. Until your feet hurt. Sing. Until your lungs hurt. Act. Until you're William Hurt." And who could forget the timeless, "You can tell a lot about a person from their biography." But wait, there's more!

Alexa Skill User: This is the year 2025. Welcome. You're the first one here.


Start your day with an inspirational list of quotes. When using the skill, you can say "Alexa, next" to move to the next quote. At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the skill.
This skill was created using a Skill Blueprint. Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
